      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, showing clear signs of being well-cared for and maintained. It's a reliable, sharp-looking ride that's ready for all your adventures, offering a smooth performance that you can count on every day!",
      "price": 34500.0,
