    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some typical signs of use like minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics functioning as they should and only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. It drives smoothly and has a documented service history, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road.",
