    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or age. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all systems functioning exactly as they should and a complete service history to back it up. You will not find a more well-preserved example of this model.",
      "price": 49900.0,
