      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in absolute showroom condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment, its mechanical integrity is beyond reproach. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a specimen of uncompromising quality and provenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
